{"tid":1957697,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"警公園「傾談」一小時始拘男生","createTime":"2020-04-04T05:56:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-04T07:29:17.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"84a426a0dbb4ee3dc73fe3e501497da3270d8129","tid":1957697,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T05:56:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200404/2L7YUXXWW23K4PEQSKKAQZOV2Y/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200404%2F2L7YUXXWW23K4PEQSKKAQZOV2Y%2F&d=dfx5yx0%2Fy135WOof7TdQym2%2BFslq3%2Bj4herl9tsBg9w%3D&h=d095d335\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200404%2F2L7YUXXWW23K4PEQSKKAQZOV2Y%2F&h=f1d31c7e\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200404/2L7YUXXWW23K4PEQSKKAQZOV2Y/</a><br />\n<br />\n警公園「傾談」一小時始拘男生<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200404/large/1585932279_58d3.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200404%2Flarge%2F1585932279_58d3.gif&h=da72e441&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大埔警署於4月1日被人投擲懷疑汽油彈，停車場空地及鐵閘被熏黑。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【汽油彈襲警署案】<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】大埔警署日前凌晨被人投擲汽油彈熏黑，三名中學男生其後被拘控縱火及襲警，昨提堂。其中夜班兼職工作的16歲學生，案發後不足十分鐘在附近公園被截停，警員與他「傾談」超過一小時後作拘捕，但證物沒有他的指模。三人不准保釋，繼續還柙。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n證物沒被告指模<br />\n<br />\n被告曾華錕、羅聶峰（均18歲）及郭姓學生（16歲）同被控4月1日燒毀警署外牆及鐵閘，曾另被控襲擊警長X，羅涉襲擊高級警員Y。裁判官張潔宜不准三人保釋，押後至5月28日再訊，待警方檢驗證物及被告手機。<br />\n<br />\n據知，曾與羅當場遭警署內衝出的X及Y拘捕。八分鐘後在500米外的公園，有警員截停郭「傾談」逾句鐘才拘捕。郭稱沒去過警署，他身上亦搜不出打火機或玻璃樽，但被捕時電話不斷收到訊息追問其行蹤位置。三名被告在警誡下保持緘默，沒有招認。<br />\n<br />\n據知辯方發現，控方案情所述公園閉路電視中人衣着，與郭被捕時的衣着不同，控方終允將針對郭的部份改為「一名男子」，修改後案情對郭未有具體指控。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：TC435/20"},{"pid":"3b28fedf0371c1bedd5ddd90d466ca3fa6ac0e8b","tid":1957697,"uid":82640,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T05:59:18.000Z","msg":"就咁睇啲狗搵人自己放火都寫得出呢啲內容<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咩舉證嚟"},{"pid":"290ac97f3795c7f2b3bb48a92f6c9d494cdfa5d9","tid":1957697,"uid":214580,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T06:05:53.000Z","msg":"法律已死"},{"pid":"7744044586bc9689a877a890d5036d5cf1bb36a3","tid":1957697,"uid":36441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T06:13:42.000Z","msg":"用手腳傾談？"},{"pid":"e150cf6cba59213ad20dc2c0ecbc69a1ce2c73ed","tid":1957697,"uid":47356,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T06:15:33.000Z","msg":"無做過點認, 戇鳩記者食屎大"},{"pid":"5b51d66ed4ff1fd000defabd3f74967f97b4e8e4","tid":1957697,"uid":8948,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T06:17:38.000Z","msg":"咁都唔俾保釋？ 理由係乜？ 定法官連剝奪一個人自由嘅理由都唔洗交代？"},{"pid":"676478be5ee63465888f4041fbfed1916c85fbf8","tid":1957697,"uid":273218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T06:27:20.000Z","msg":"睇唔到警署比人燒<br />\n只係同白衫人同埋極權中共軍政府分部比人燒"},{"pid":"59fff084d0cf86350a7789765c2a89432c9084fc","tid":1957697,"uid":54721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T06:43:58.000Z","msg":"根本收工返屋企行過<br />\n咁耐未返到屋企梗係SEND訊息追問其行蹤位置<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ac596a42d7aeefb903029168dcd4e4e71c7443d","tid":1957697,"uid":38666,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"5b51d66ed4ff1fd000defabd3f74967f97b4e8e4","tid":1957697,"uid":8948,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T06:17:38.000Z","msg":"咁都唔俾保釋？ 理由係乜？ 定法官連剝奪一個人自由嘅理由都唔洗交代？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T07:29:17.000Z","msg":"警員誠實可靠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}